            <lg xml:id="TK135">
<l>aḻukkā ṟuṭaiyāṉka ṇākkampōṉ ṟillai</l>
<l>yoḻukka milāṉka ṇuyarvu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As wealth to one possessed of envy, to one without</l>
<l>propriety high status never comes.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
